    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于 Shadow of Ancients</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Shadow of Ancients》是一款拥有风格化且色彩鲜明氛围的 3D 半开放世界叙事冒险游戏。故事发生在一座岛上小镇，年轻的 Aiden 的人生即将被卷入未知冒险。他体内寄宿着一个名为“图尤克”的上古恶魔，而他本人却毫不知情。玩家将体验这段强大、不可预测、且并非始终受控的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/d66c287f04958a8c1ac779d207bbde26.poster.avif?t=1771883321\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/d66c287f04958a8c1ac779d207bbde26.webm?t=1771883321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>试玩版内容（公开版 – 10月18日）</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第一幕部分内容：序章任务、探索以及多种战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实时战斗：闪避、技能释放、轻/重攻击</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恶魔形态与 Boss 战：Aiden 会在某些时刻失控，短暂无法操作；甚至在失控期间，玩家需要以敌方身份战斗</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集与制作：收集植物与素材，酿造各类药剂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自然氛围的风格化世界：穿越森林小径、遗迹与地下洞窟</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/263d6196ae8b1f10769cc5e83666920a.avif?t=1771883321\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完整版核心愿景</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事为先，但选择权在玩家：Aiden 的旅程会因抉择而改变人际关系与背后真相</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流畅而有打击感的战斗：升级、技能构建与扎实的对抗体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重新设计的界面：更清晰、更直观的 UI/UX</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有目的的探索：更多富有意义的支线任务、跑酷、解谜与追逐</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集、成长、生存：利用动植物资源推进游戏核心系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动漫风格卡通渲染：延续并强化受现代风格化 RPG 启发的清晰视觉风格</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/958c0b6d6672f19493870274c3a02189.avif?t=1771883321\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为何发布试玩版</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本次提前公开旨在收集玩家反馈。无论是操作体验、界面、预期差异还是性能问题，我们面前仍有大量工作，而目标是让游戏朝着玩家真正乐于体验的方向发展。希望从玩家角度听见我们未察觉之处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/064a69c6330d66c948a6bac1fb0588da.poster.avif?t=1771883321\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/064a69c6330d66c948a6bac1fb0588da.webm?t=1771883321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>反馈指引</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哪些地方造成困惑？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗体验如何？你期望它应当如何？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >哪些任务/区域让你投入？哪些没有？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可在 Steam 讨论区反馈，或通过游戏内/启动器的反馈入口提交（上线后开放），亦可通过 Reddit / LinkedIn 联系</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bug 报告、功能建议、预期落差……任何信息都将影响正式版的成型</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/43773b64b2310740cd97335fd904d765.poster.avif?t=1771883321\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/43773b64b2310740cd97335fd904d765.webm?t=1771883321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开发路线提示</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩版中存在仍需调整的部分与内容空缺（占位文本/UI，部分设备性能波动等）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将依据反馈快速迭代，并通过补丁推送更新</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢试玩我们的首个公开 Demo。如看好本作，请加入愿望单并关注进度，这对团队意义重大</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/5b233e7fc9cd20a023207d384c32091b.poster.avif?t=1771883321\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273380/extras/5b233e7fc9cd20a023207d384c32091b.webm?t=1771883321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
